      "title": "Power outage time is likely to increase",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Front Socialist Party has warned that there is a possibility of a 14-hour power supply ban in the country.",
        "The Education Secretary of the Front Socialist Party Bubutu Jayagoda said that the Electricity Board has informed the Treasury that it needs 320 million US dollars for the purchase of coal."
      ],
